## ğŸ§¾ Sample Scenario I Simulated

**Finding:** CVE-2023-XXXX on Windows Server  
**Source:** Mock WSUS Vulnerability Scan  
**Risk:** Critical  
**System Impacted:** WIN-DC-02

**POA&M Entry Practice:**

| Field | Example |
|-------|---------|
| Weakness ID | WSUS-CVE-2023-001 |
| Description | Remote code execution vulnerability |
| Source | Mock WSUS scan |
| Scheduled Completion Date | 2024-09-01 |
| Milestones | 1. Patch applied by 08/20, 2. Validation by 08/25 |
| Status | In Progress |
| Evidence | Placeholder for scan screenshot or remediation ticket |

This exercise helped me understand the workflow that analysts, ISSOs, and auditors follow when tracking unresolved findings.

